@startuml myweatherdata_state_process
!theme plain
skinparam shadowing false

[*] --> Idle

Idle --> ValidationFailed : start with invalid input\n[FR_15, FR_16]
ValidationFailed --> Idle : input corrected

Idle --> Running : start with valid input\n[FR_17]

Running --> Error_Station : station not found\n[FR_03, FR_18]
Running --> Error_Fetch : dwd fetch failed\n[FR_06, FR_18]
Running --> Error_Export : png path/tech error\n[FR_23, FR_24]

Running --> EmptyData : no visualization data\n[FR_21]
EmptyData --> Running : new valid request

Running --> Completed : import/export/visualization done\n[FR_17]
Completed --> Running : restart process\n[FR_17]

Error_Station --> Running : retry
Error_Fetch --> Running : retry
Error_Export --> Running : retry

Completed --> [*]

note right of Running
Aktive Verarbeitung mit Schrittzuordnung.
FR-Referenzen: FR_17, FR_18
end note

@enduml
